dct_title_s: Map of land-grant and bond-aided railroads of the United States
dct_description_sm: Map and text were intended for use as an official guide by the military in order to receive compensation for transportation of U.S. troops and property over land-grant and bond-aided railroads.; Accompanied by guide/text (61 pages ; 20 cm.). Text contains government regulations and tables of railroads.
